<div class="registration-form small-10 medium-8 large-6 centered columns">
  <h1>
  Farm to Foodie
  </h1>
  <h5>
    <strong>Welcome!</strong><br> Thanks for stopping by.<br>Check out these
    restaurants who source their menus locally, <br>Thanks again for supporting your local farmers.<br><br>
    <strong><em>Local Food, thousands of miles fresher!</em></strong>
  </h5>
  <strong><h3></h3></strong><br><br>
  <div class="farm-buttons" >
    <% if @restaurants.length > 0 %>
      <% @restaurants.shuffle.each do |restaurant| %>
          <div class="farm-details small-3 centered columns">
            <%= link_to "#{restaurant.name}", restaurant_path(restaurant), class: "registration-form button round tiny" %><br>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <p>So far, no restaurants have signed up to source their food locally.
      If you would like to encourage your favorite restaurant to consider sourcing their food like this, talk to the manager about signing up.</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
